Synopsis: Tests whether an OpenAI Assistant ID exists.
Description: The Test-OAIAssistantId function checks whether an OpenAI Assistant ID exists by querying the Get-OAIAssistantItem cmdlet.
Inputs: None. You cannot pipe objects to this function.
Outputs:
System.Boolean
Returns $true if the Assistant ID exists, otherwise returns $false.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Test-OAIAssistantId -AssistantId "12345678"
Checks whether the Assistant ID "12345678" exists.
